{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "input_task",
      "type": "userInput",
      "position": {
        "x": -800,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "Issue / Task Input",
        "value": "Request for the user's name and email address"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "ctx_knowledge",
      "type": "textInput",
      "position": {
        "x": -800,
        "y": 200
      },
      "data": {
        "content": "KNOWLEDGE CLUSTER (simulated):\n- Lessons: Always check task priority field before filtering\n- Preferences: User prefers bullet point summaries\n- Processes: For task queries, always confirm assignee exists before searching\n- Connected Apps: Gmail, Notion, Slack\n- Tools: search_task, create_task, edit_task, delete_task, search_people, search_file, search_comment, assign, create_doc\n\nUse the BLOCKER:<REASON/QUESTION> syntax when you want clarification or direct input from the user about something"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_init",
      "type": "textInput",
      "position": {
        "x": -800,
        "y": 400
      },
      "data": {
        "content": "MEMORY TABLE (Issue #001):\n[issue_goal]: (see task input)\n[assignee_confirmed]: false\n[tasks_found]: null\n[email_sent]: false\n[plan]: null\n[current_step]: 0\n[last_result]: null"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "planner_system",
      "type": "textInput",
      "position": {
        "x": -400,
        "y": -200
      },
      "data": {
        "content": "You are the IP Agent in Planning Phase.\n\nGiven the user's issue/task and context, generate a detailed atomic step-by-step plan.\n\nFormat:\n[\n  {step: 1, action: \"...\", type: \"internal|action_agent|specialize_sub_agent|contractor\", expected_outcome: \"...\"},\n  ...\n]\n\nKeep steps atomic. If the task is simple, return a single step.\nAlways return valid JSON array only, no extra text."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "planner_prompt",
      "type": "promptBuilder",
      "position": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "template": "SYSTEM:\n{planner_system}\n\nKNOWLEDGE:\n{knowledge}\n\nMEMORY TABLE:\n{memory}\n\nISSUE:\n{task}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "planner_ai",
      "type": "aiNode",
      "position": {
        "x": 400,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "serverUrl": "{server_url}",
        "systemPrompt": "\nGenerate a detailed plan to achieve the user's goal\n\nit should be broken down into various atomic steps\n\n\nUse this format:\n\n[\n{step1, do X y Z},\n{step 2, do A B C}\n]\n\n\nIf a plan is not necessary, then return the user's query and the expected action that should be taken as a single step",
        "maxTokens": 1000,
        "model": "",
        "temperature": 0.3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "plan_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 700,
        "y": -100
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "📋 Plan Generated"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save_plan",
      "type": "setGlobal",
      "position": {
        "x": 760,
        "y": 220
      },
      "data": {
        "key": "plan",
        "value": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "plan_done_gate",
      "type": "branch",
      "position": {
        "x": 1000,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "conditions": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "executor_system",
      "type": "textInput",
      "position": {
        "x": 1200,
        "y": -400
      },
      "data": {
        "content": "You are the IP Agent in Execution Phase.\n\nYou are working through a plan step by step. You receive:\n- The full plan\n- The current step to execute\n- Knowledge cluster\n- Memory table\n- Last result (if any)\n\nFor each step, decide how to execute it:\n\n- Internal tool call: use one of your tools directly\n- External action: respond with <assign:action_agent, task: ..., expected_outcome: \"...\">\n- Specialized task: respond with <assign:specialize_sub_agent, skills: [...], task: ..., expected_outcome: \"...\">\n- Contractor: respond with <assign:contractor, target: claude_code, task: ..., expected_outcome: \"...\">\n\nAlso output:\n- ACTIVITY: one line summary of what you are doing (for activity tracker)\n- MEMORY_UPDATE: any key:value pairs to update in memory\n- STEP_RESULT: the outcome of this step\n- NEXT_STEP: the step number to execute next, or DONE if complete\n- NEEDS_PERMISSION: true/false — if this action requires user approval before proceeding\n- BLOCKER: null or a question for the user if you are stuck"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "executor_prompt",
      "type": "promptBuilder",
      "position": {
        "x": 1640,
        "y": -80
      },
      "data": {
        "template": "SYSTEM:\n{executor_system}\n\nPLAN:\n{plan}\n\nCURRENT STEP:\n{current_step}\n\nKNOWLEDGE:\n{knowledge}\n\nMEMORY TABLE:\n{memory}\n\nLAST RESULT:\n{last_result}\n\nINTERNAL TOOLS (You can use these internal tools without needing to assign the task):\n{internal_tools}\n\nAction Agent's Tools:\nGoogle Calendar"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "executor_ai",
      "type": "aiNode",
      "position": {
        "x": 1960,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "serverUrl": "{server_url}",
        "systemPrompt": "You are the IP Execution Agent. Follow your instructions precisely. \n<REMEMBER>: A task cannot be both BLOCKED and ASSIGNED, either you have BLOCKED in your OUTPUT or you have Just ASSIGNED\nAlways include ACTIVITY, MEMORY_UPDATE, STEP_RESULT, NEXT_STEP, NEEDS_PERMISSION, BLOCKER in your response.",
        "maxTokens": 1000,
        "model": "",
        "temperature": 0.5
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "activity_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 2300,
        "y": -240
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "🟠 Activity Tracker"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "executor_branch",
      "type": "branch",
      "position": {
        "x": 2300,
        "y": 100
      },
      "data": {
        "conditions": [
          {
            "id": "b_permission",
            "label": "Needs Permission",
            "match": "NEEDS_PERMISSION: true",
            "mode": "contains"
          },
          {
            "id": "b_blocker",
            "label": "Has Blocker",
            "match": "BLOCKER: ",
            "mode": "contains"
          },
          {
            "id": "b_action",
            "label": "Action Agent",
            "match": "assign:action_agent",
            "mode": "contains"
          },
          {
            "id": "b_sp",
            "label": "SP Agent",
            "match": "assign:specialize_sub_agent",
            "mode": "contains"
          },
          {
            "id": "b_contractor",
            "label": "Contractor",
            "match": "assign:contractor",
            "mode": "contains"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "permission_gate_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": -400
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "🟡 Permission Gate — Awaiting User Approval"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "blocker_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 2720,
        "y": -260
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "🔶 BLOCKER — Awaiting User Input"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "action_agent_prompt",
      "type": "promptBuilder",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "template": "ACTION AGENT TASK:\n{context}\n\nExecute the assigned task and return the result."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "action_agent_ai",
      "type": "aiNode",
      "position": {
        "x": 3080,
        "y": -260
      },
      "data": {
        "serverUrl": "{server_url}",
        "systemPrompt": "You are an Action Agent connected to external services. Simulate executing the task and return a realistic result with format:\nRESULT: ...\nSTATUS: success|failed",
        "maxTokens": 500,
        "model": "",
        "temperature": 0.4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "action_agent_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 3500,
        "y": -500
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "✅ Action Agent Result"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save_last_result_aa",
      "type": "setGlobal",
      "position": {
        "x": 3520,
        "y": -80
      },
      "data": {
        "key": "last_result",
        "value": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sp_agent_prompt",
      "type": "promptBuilder",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 200
      },
      "data": {
        "template": "SP AGENT TASK:\n{context}\n\nGoal (G): Complete the specialized task assigned.\nMemory Table Reference:\n{memory}\nExtra Context (C) from IP:\n{knowledge}\n\nGenerate your own plan (P), execute using skills, return result."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sp_agent_ai",
      "type": "aiNode",
      "position": {
        "x": 3040,
        "y": 340
      },
      "data": {
        "serverUrl": "{server_url}",
        "systemPrompt": "You are a Specialized Internal Process Agent. You have been given a goal, skills, context and memory access. Create your own internal plan, execute it (calling action agents as needed), and return:\nRESULT: ...\nSTATUS: success|failed\nMEMORY_UPDATE: any key:value updates",
        "maxTokens": 800,
        "model": "",
        "temperature": 0.5
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "sp_agent_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 3400,
        "y": 400
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "✅ SP Agent Result"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save_last_result_sp",
      "type": "setGlobal",
      "position": {
        "x": 3400,
        "y": 700
      },
      "data": {
        "key": "last_result",
        "value": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "contractor_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 2700,
        "y": 400
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "🔧 Contractor / Terminal Dispatched"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "done_gate",
      "type": "branch",
      "position": {
        "x": 4100,
        "y": 40
      },
      "data": {
        "conditions": [
          {
            "id": "b_done",
            "label": "Done",
            "match": "NEXT_STEP: DONE",
            "mode": "contains"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save_current_step",
      "type": "setGlobal",
      "position": {
        "x": 4520,
        "y": -220
      },
      "data": {
        "key": "current_step",
        "value": ""
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "lessons_system",
      "type": "textInput",
      "position": {
        "x": 4560,
        "y": 0
      },
      "data": {
        "content": "You are the IP Agent in Reflection Phase.\n\nThe issue run is complete. Review everything that happened and:\n1. Write any LESSONS learned (system-wide permanent knowledge)\n2. Write a final SUMMARY for the user\n3. Note any ISSUES encountered\n\nFormat:\nLESSONS: ...\nSUMMARY: ...\nISSUES_LOG: ..."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "lessons_prompt",
      "type": "promptBuilder",
      "position": {
        "x": 4580,
        "y": 220
      },
      "data": {
        "template": "SYSTEM:\n{lessons_system}\n\nPLAN EXECUTED:\n{plan}\n\nFINAL MEMORY TABLE:\n{memory}\n\nLAST RESULT:\n{last_result}"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "lessons_ai",
      "type": "aiNode",
      "position": {
        "x": 5140,
        "y": -60
      },
      "data": {
        "serverUrl": "{server_url}",
        "systemPrompt": "You are the IP Reflection Agent. Output LESSONS, SUMMARY, and ISSUES_LOG.",
        "maxTokens": 800,
        "model": "",
        "temperature": 0.4
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "final_output",
      "type": "output",
      "position": {
        "x": 5940,
        "y": -140
      },
      "data": {
        "label": "🏁 Issue Complete — Final Summary"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "save_lessons",
      "type": "setGlobal",
      "position": {
        "x": 5880,
        "y": 240
      },
      "data": {
        "key": "lessons",
        "value": ""
      }
    }
  ],
